{"tid":2045864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參與抗議示威活動 紐約市長白思豪女兒被捕","createTime":"2020-06-01T05:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T05:31:06.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7909edd39d5241c47f8d5dada7cd575fea8c29","tid":2045864,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕佛洛伊德（George Floyd）死亡案引發全美各地發生抗疫及示威活動，部份活動更演變成暴動，多座城市以實施宵禁及調動國民兵來因應暴動。然而紐約市內也不乏多起抗議活動，不過紐約市執法人員透露，紐約市長白思豪（Bill de Blasio）的女兒席亞拉（Chiara de Blasio）於週六晚間被逮捕，原因是參加非法集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/01/php6LlrAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F01%2Fphp6LlrAE.jpg&h=08089d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，消息人士指出，席亞拉於當地時間週六晚間10點30分在曼哈頓下城的東12街和百老匯一帶被捕。消息人士指出，當時席亞拉參與的抗議活動約有百人規模，當中有人朝警方丟擲物品，而席亞拉當時並沒有朝警方投擲物品，她之所以被捕，是因為當時警察命令她離開時拒絕離開。<br />\n<br />\n席亞拉遭到逮捕之後，在地址上填寫白思豪在紐約市上東城的「格雷西大廈」住所，不過席亞拉並沒有告知警察她是市長的女兒，隨後便被警方釋放。<br />\n<br />\n在席亞拉被捕後，白思豪恰巧正在發表呼籲紐約市民回家的談話。白思豪強調，市府已聽到大家的訴求，但「現在該回家了」，「若是為了表達暴力或仇視警察的人，當你做出暴力行為時將會被逮捕」。紐約市政府於週日晚間拒絕評論席亞拉遭逮一事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3183416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3183416&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=325b9e7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3183416&h=9fb37fa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3183416</a>"},{"pid":"fc2d324bf16eb42d66d93bdd3b72eeb06a63c208","tid":2045864,"uid":44823,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"美國梁齊昕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58382d7c34d4382005e7b295ef47594da45327e","tid":2045864,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"「若是為了表達暴力或仇視警察的人，當你做出暴力行為時將會被逮捕」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e91a9b0b64f52f9d283938c8bfa44d8309ec02","tid":2045864,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bde087a1d331f4070cd38e3a3b9bce931afd72","tid":2045864,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"黃種人生個黑人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3b37b66a6aa19d2b60b5d0715e97edde194ea9","tid":2045864,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d3bde087a1d331f4070cd38e3a3b9bce931afd72","tid":2045864,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"黃種人生個黑人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:18:52.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黃種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595e9f26e59212b7d4c9b539308125c17d564fa3","tid":2045864,"uid":171273,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d3bde087a1d331f4070cd38e3a3b9bce931afd72","tid":2045864,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"黃種人生個黑人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"佢老婆係黑人 幾出名既左翼作家黎"},{"pid":"3b34ac909eb90d949a46625407601f6be1acf11f","tid":2045864,"uid":75823,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家最熟悉既野"},{"pid":"5cbe2fd726710ca4affa993cfaa88f6b664053d7","tid":2045864,"uid":54876,"like":2,"dislike":1